Package: axon
Version: __VERSION__
Section: utils
Priority: optional
Architecture: all
Depends: curl
Maintainer: suphakin-th <suphakin.th@gmail.com>
Homepage: https://github.com/suphakin-th/axon
Description: Universal CI/CD scaffold for GitHub Actions and GitLab CI
 axon scaffolds production-ready GitHub Actions and GitLab CI pipelines
 for any language or framework.
 .
 Run "axon init" in any project directory to scaffold CI/CD files
 immediately. Supports Node.js, Python, Go, PHP, Java, Ruby, .NET,
 and any language that runs in Docker.
